WikiText-2 (raw v1) — license and attribution
=============================================

The file `wiki.test.raw` in this directory is the test split of the
WikiText-2 raw v1 corpus, redistributed here under its original licence
to provide a reproducible default evaluation corpus for `mlx-kld`'s
`--long` streamed mode.

Source
------
- Paper: Stephen Merity, Caiming Xiong, James Bradbury, Richard Socher.
  "Pointer Sentinel Mixture Models". ICLR 2017.
  https://arxiv.org/abs/1609.07843
- Original release: Salesforce Research.
- This file mirrors the version distributed at:
  https://huggingface.co/datasets/ggml-org/ci/resolve/main/wikitext-2-raw-v1.zip
  (the same archive used by llama.cpp's `scripts/get-wikitext-2.sh`).

Underlying content
------------------
WikiText-2 is derived from verified Good and Featured articles on the
English Wikipedia. Wikipedia text is dual-licensed under the
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International Licence
(CC BY-SA 4.0) and the GNU Free Documentation Licence (GFDL).

