Why it lives here
-----------------
Bundling the corpus avoids a runtime download dependency, makes the
`--long` mode reproducible offline, and matches the corpus used by
llama.cpp's `llama-perplexity` so numbers are at least methodologically
comparable to published llama.cpp scoreboards.
